                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The thought of burning stoves and freshly cooked food is comforting indeed, but a chef can't be cooking all the time, nor is an adventurer's appetite without limit! Filling the gaps between meals with exciting Genius Invokation TCG duels is another good way to stay warm in the mountains...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: Your Support Zone starts with 1 \"Xudong\" card.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Hint: When Xudong is on the field, you can spend 2 less Elemental Dice to play a Food Card each Round!",
